43	## Sections
44	
45	| Order | Section | Widget Type | Description |
46	|---|---|---|---|
47	| 1 | Progress Chart | Card + Line Chart | Line chart with 1W/1M/All toggle |
48	| 2 | Latest Entry Card | Card | Today's weight with delta |
49	| 3 | Nutrition Tips Card | Card (lavender tint bg) | Stage-specific tips with week badge |
50	| 4 | Weight Log List | SliverList | All entries sorted by date desc |
51	| 5 (overlay) | Add Weight Sheet | showModalBottomSheet | Form with weight, date, notes fields |
52	| 6 (overlay) | Entry Detail Sheet | showModalBottomSheet | View/edit/delete existing entry |
53	
54	## Interactive Elements
55	
56	| Element | Type | Behavior |
57	|---|---|---|
58	| Back button | Button | Navigate back |
59	| Toggle chips | Chip group | Filter chart data by time range |
60	| Latest Entry Card | Display | None (display-only) |
61	| Nutrition Tips Card | Card | Expandable (optional for MVP) |
62	| Log list items | Card | Tap → detail sheet, Long-press → edit/delete sheet |
63	| FAB | FloatingActionButton | Open add weight bottom sheet |
64	
65	## Data Entities
66	
67	### WeightEntry
68	```dart
69	class WeightEntry {
70	  String id;
71	  DateTime date;
72	  double value; // in user's preferred unit
73	  String? notes;
74	}
75	```
76	
77	### Providers
78	- `WeightEntryProvider` — entries list, selectedRange, CRUD operations
79	- `PregnancyProfileProvider` — currentWeek for nutrition tips
80	- `UserPreferencesProvider` — units (kg/lbs)
81	
82	## Animation Specs
83	
84	| Animation | Duration | Curve |
85	|---|---|---|
86	| Screen push | 300ms | ease-in-out |
87	| Card fade-in | 200ms | ease-out |
88	| List stagger | 50ms delay per item | ease-out |
89	| FAB fade-in | 200ms | ease-out |
90	| Bottom sheet | 250ms | ease-out |
91	| Chip selection | 150ms | opacity |
92	| FAB press | 200ms | scale 90% |
93	
94	## Accessibility
95	
96	- Semantic labels on all interactive elements
97	- 48dp minimum touch targets
98	- Screen reader announcements for state changes
99	- Color contrast: AA compliant for all text/background pairs
100	
101	## Anti-Patterns
102	
103	- No GridView for weight log (use SliverList)
104	- No BottomNavigationBar (hidden per UX spec)
105	- No hard-coded weight units
106	- FAB positioned bottom-right only
107	- No animation on initial FAB load without fade-in
